{"tid":1715987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大宣布停課至學期末","createTime":"2019-11-13T08:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:04:09.000Z","uid":258328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"32eea86246a27e6612b9d1b7622ed4c5e8f7a5e9","tid":1715987,"uid":258328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:31:11.000Z","msg":"Message from Prof Lionel NI, Provost<br />\n=============================<br />\n <br />\nDear Students,<br />\n <br />\nGiven the escalation of unrest at sister universities last night, the management has decided to temporarily change the University&rsquo;s mode of instruction. For the remaining two and a half weeks of the term, there will NOT be any face-to-face classes or any proctored on-campus final examination on the Clear Water Bay campus. Classes will be conducted through on-line means starting next week.  Final examinations or alternate arrangements will be announced by the instructors of the courses.  This will accommodate students who may want to leave campus before the end of the term. Faculty members of individual courses will email students on more detailed arrangements of their courses.<br />\n <br />\nSincerely,<br />\nLionel NI<br />\nProvost"},{"pid":"ac4d9d1863a0bae8cc3430b5a30362f3c77ddf8e","tid":1715987,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:31:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9DDrPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9DDrPs.jpg&h=fd5eb776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQHwOww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQHwOww.jpg&h=056adf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"5dca6026027cee3f2eb9aee703fd31f806455cea","tid":1715987,"uid":258328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:32:34.000Z","msg":"收到風兩個星期都唔會完？"},{"pid":"a7d85cab233889fe8f834a70d09ae44fd835b91d","tid":1715987,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"次次連登都係自己製造恐慌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1716010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1716010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6cf079febba6140cdbe9d757cdcf8c26009324bd","tid":1715987,"uid":172290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"仲要人上堂考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788c8ca9145179de0d633ffd86a95053f0766470","tid":1715987,"uid":300165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf079febba6140cdbe9d757cdcf8c26009324bd","tid":1715987,"uid":172290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"仲要人上堂考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:04:09.000Z","msg":"online 堂，知識都重要性"}]}